  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# **Laser Rate Equation â€“ Bifurcation Analysis**\n",
    "This notebook analyzes the nondimensional laser rate equations:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$ x' = x (y - 1), \\qquad y' = -\\alpha y - \\alpha x y + \\alpha \\beta. $$\n",
    "\n",
    "Parameters:\n",
    "- $\\alpha > 0$  (ratio of decay rates)\n",
    "- $\\beta$ (dimensionless pump parameter)\n",
    "\n",
    "We will:\n",
    "* nondimensionalize the system\n",
    * compute fixed points\n",
    * analyze stability\n",
    * generate phase portraits\n",
    * generate a stability diagram and bifurcation curves\n"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "imports"
   },
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from scipy.integrate import solve_ivp\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "sns.set(style='whitegrid', context='notebook')"
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": []
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## **Define the nondimensional laser system**"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "def laser_system(t, z, alpha, beta):\n",
    "    x, y = z\n",
    "    dx = x * (y - 1)\n",
    "    dy = -alpha * y - alpha * x * y + alpha * beta\n",
    "    return [dx, dy]"
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": []
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## **Fixed Points**\n",
    "$$E_0 = (0, \\beta)$$\n",
    "$$E_L = (\\beta - 1, 1), \\quad (\n",
    " \\beta > 1)$$"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "def fixed_points(alpha, beta):\n",
    "    E0 = np.array([0, beta])\n",
    "    EL = None\n",
    "    if beta > 1:\n",
    "        EL = np.array([beta - 1, 1])\n",
    "    return E0, EL\n",
    "\n",
    "fixed_points(1.0, 2.0)"
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": []
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## **Phase Portrait Plotter**"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "def phase_portrait(alpha, beta, title=None):\n",
    "    x = np.linspace(0, max(4, beta+2), 30)\n",
    "    y = np.linspace(0, max(4, beta+2), 30)\n",
    "    X, Y = np.meshgrid(x, y)\n",
    "    U = X * (Y - 1)\n",
    "    V = -alpha * Y - alpha * X * Y + alpha * beta\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))\n",
    "    plt.streamplot(X, Y, U, V, density=1.1, linewidth=0.7, arrowsize=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "    E0, EL = fixed_points(alpha, beta)\n",
    "    plt.scatter(E0[0], E0[1], s=80, color='blue', label='E0: trivial eq.')\n",
    "    if EL is not None:\n",
    "        plt.scatter(EL[0], EL[1], s=80, color='red', label='EL: lasing eq.')\n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.xlabel('$x$ (scaled photons)')\n",
    "    plt.ylabel('$y$ (scaled atoms)')\n",
    "    plt.legend()\n",
    "    plt.title(title or f'Phase Portrait (alpha={alpha}, beta={beta})')\n",
    "    plt.show()"
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": []
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## **Example Phase Portraits**"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "phase_portrait(alpha=1.0, beta=0.5, title='Below threshold (beta < 1)')\n",
    "phase_portrait(alpha=1.0, beta=1.0, title='At threshold (beta = 1)')\n",
    "phase_portrait(alpha=1.0, beta=2.0, title='Above threshold (beta > 1)')"
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": []
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## **Stability & Bifurcation Stability Curve**\n",
    "The stability boundary between nodes and spirals is:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\Delta = 0 \\quad \\Longleftrightarrow \\quad\n",
    "    \\alpha = \\frac{4(\\beta - 1)}{\\beta^2}.\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "beta_vals = np.linspace(1.0, 5.0, 400)\n",
    "alpha_curve = 4*(beta_vals - 1)/beta_vals**2\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8,5))\n",
    "plt.plot(beta_vals, alpha_curve, label='Node/Spiral boundary')\n",
    "plt.axvline(1, color='red', linestyle='--', label='Laser threshold (beta=1)')\n",
    "plt.ylim(0, 2)\n",
    "plt.xlabel('$\\beta$ (pump)')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('$\\alpha$ (decay ratio)')\n",
    "plt.title('Stability Diagram of the Lasing Equilibrium')\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": []
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## **Conclusion**\n",
    "* For $\\beta<1$: Only the trivial equilibrium exists and is stable.\n",
    "* At $\\beta=1$: A transcritical bifurcation.\n",
    "* For $\\beta>1$: The lasing equilibrium is stable (node or spiral).\n",
    "\n",
    "This reproduces the standard laser threshold bifurcation described in Milonni & Eberly, Haken, and Strogatz."
   ]
  }

